Package: zephyr
Architecture: any
Depends:
	${shlibs:Depends},
	${misc:Depends}
Description: Go-based CLI project template (example: puff1)
 zephyr is a template for small command-line tools written in Go. It
 currently ships the puff1 example (a cat-like utility) with Debian
 metadata, man page, bash completion, and GNU gettext .po files embedded
 in the published binary for offline translations.
